{"word":"ἐργάτης","slug":"ἐργάτης","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ἐργάτης, ου, ὁ</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἔργον\">ἔργον</a></el>]<b><p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>1.</pp></b> ‘one engaged in work’, <b>worker, laborer<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>a.</pp></b> of <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ pers.\">pers.</a> engaged in physical labor <b><a href='B:470 9:37'>Mt 9:37</a>; <a href='B:470 10:10'>10:10</a>;</b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ cp.\">cp.</a> <b><a href='B:510 19:25'>Ac 19:25</a>.<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>b.</pp></b> by extension, of spiritual leaders <b><a href='B:540 11:13'>2 Cor 11:13</a>; <a href='B:570 3:2'>Phil 3:2</a>; <a href='B:620 2:15'>2 Ti 2:15</a>.<p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>2.</pp></b> ‘one who produces <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ someth.\">someth.</a> through work’, <b>doer,</b> in satire <el>τῆς ἀδιϰίας ἐ.</el> expert in iniquity <b><a href='B:490 13:27'>Lk 13:27</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:ἐργασία\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:ἔργον\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}